This map is made for the KSF server, or any server with a similar surf-timer mod. I intend to create a jail version of the map for regular surf servers soon.

*Original Post*

I'm being honest with you, this is my first map released. I am VERY proud of this map, because it has taken me over a month, and over 7 keyboard and 2 monitors.

This map is BIG. I didn't save the log, but I have used over 98% of the brushsides allowed and over 90% of brushes.

There is roughly 1:30-2minutesof surfing here, and THIS IS NOT MEANT TO BE A HARD MAP. Yes, the end is difficult, but that is meant to be the ONLY hard area.

I am not completely satisfied that this is worthy of a full release, so I'm just gonna call this beta1 :P

I would like to point out that this map is FULLY optimised! EVERYTHING apart from the skyboxes has been func_detail'd! This map is as optimized as it ever will be. If anyone wants to have a crack at optimizeign the map further, PM me for the .vmf

Any bugs you find please tell me, and any feedback whatsoever is great.

Have fun and tell me what you think :D
